# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Frontend (Vite) environment — placeholders only, no secrets.
#
# NOTE: Vite inlines VITE_* variables at BUILD time. In production these are
# baked into the static bundle, so VITE_API_URL must be provided when the
# frontend image is BUILT (build arg), not at Cloud Run runtime.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Base URL of the backend API + Socket.IO server.
# Local dev:   http://localhost:4001
# Production:  https://<your-backend-cloud-run-url>
VITE_API_URL=
